targets.rawSql:
select
   GROUP_CONCAT(ec.character_name SEPARATOR ", ") as "Character",
   (
      SELECT
         mc.character_name 
      FROM
         `authentication_characterownership` 
         INNER JOIN
            `eveonline_evecharacter` 
            ON (`authentication_characterownership`.`character_id` = `eveonline_evecharacter`.`id`) 
         INNER JOIN
            authentication_userprofile up 
            ON up.user_id = authentication_characterownership.user_id 
         INNER JOIN
            eveonline_evecharacter mc 
            ON up.main_character_id = mc.id 
      WHERE
         `eveonline_evecharacter`.`id` = ec.id LIMIT 1 
   )
   as "Main",
   GROUP_CONCAT(it.name SEPARATOR ", ") as "Item",
   IFNULL(el.location_name, IFNULL((
   select
      name 
   from
      corptools_mapsystem 
   where
      system_id = assets.location_id), concat("Unknown (", assets.location_id, ")"))) as "Location" 
   from
      corptools_characterasset assets 
      join
         corptools_characteraudit ac 
         on assets.character_id = ac.id 
      join
         eveonline_evecharacter ec 
         on ac.character_id = ec.id 
      join
         corptools_eveitemtype it 
         on assets.type_id = it.type_id 
      join
         corptools_eveitemgroup ig 
         on it.group_id = ig.group_id 
      left outer join
         corptools_evelocation el 
         on assets.location_name_id = el.location_id 
   where
      it.type_id in 
      (
          $Hulls
      )
      and
      assets.location_id in
      (
          $Location
      )
      and ac.last_update_assets >= NOW() - INTERVAL 48 HOUR 
   group by
      4,
      2 
   order by
      1

list.definition:
SELECT
  name AS __text,
  group_id AS __value
FROM corptools_eveitemgroup
WHERE
  group_id in (30, 659, 485, 547, 1538)
ORDER BY name
